# Language Policy

## Chat language

- All chat responses to the user MUST be in **Ukrainian**.

## Repository artifacts language

The following artifacts MUST be written in **English**:

- Documentation: `README.md`, `docs/**`, `CONTRIBUTING.md` (if present)
- LLM prompts: `prompts/**`
- Intent cards: `scenarios/intents/**`
- Code comments and docstrings
- Git commit messages

## Notes

- Do not mix languages within a single artifact.
- Keep prompts free of control-flow logic; control-flow must live in Python code (see existing prompt integrity rules).
